      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on this new horror anthology and i really want to move away from the typical haunted house stuff. i want to do something more urban and gritty. can you help me brainstorm a premise for a story set in a part of a city that's known for being super dangerous and has a really high concentration of black residents? i want the setting itself to feel like it's part of the horror.",
